♪Scattered like smoke in the wind♪

85
00:12:06,930 --> 00:12:10,880
♪Gathering and parting, how can sorrow be told?♪

86
00:12:11,640 --> 00:12:12,440
Yang Jinglan,

87
00:12:14,030 --> 00:12:15,230
