94
00:12:32,230 --> 00:12:33,240
♪Fate parts ways and drifts afar♪

95
00:12:34,080 --> 00:12:35,000
Besides,

96
00:12:35,670 --> 00:12:37,520
your family agreed to this marriage

97
00:12:38,000 --> 00:12:39,640
to save my mother.

98
00:12:40,590 --> 00:12:41,790
If I go back on this promise,

99
00:12:43,790 --> 00:12:45,670
