100
00:12:48,030 --> 00:12:49,080
You do not need to worry about me.

101
00:12:49,080 --> 00:12:49,270
♪Cannot bloom the flowers of togetherness♪

102
00:12:52,320 --> 00:12:53,470
I will silence

103
00:12:53,470 --> 00:12:53,840
♪Where is the moonlight to answer our vows♪

104
00:12:54,840 --> 00:12:56,520
whoever dares to breathe a word of it!

105
00:12:56,520 --> 00:12:57,650
♪And to shine upon you and me♪

106
00:13:01,030 --> 00:13:02,000
Can you silence

107
00:13:02,000 --> 00:13:03,020
♪Gathering and parting, how can sorrow be told?♪

108
00:13:03,590 --> 00:13:05,910
the whole world?

109
00:13:05,910 --> 00:13:07,000
♪When will love's silk be woven into brocade?♪

110
00:13:07,640 --> 00:13:09,710
Secrets always find their way out,

111
00:13:10,520 --> 00:13:11,840
